These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
Hobby: filmmaking, gardening, drawing, card-games
1. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Hobby:filmmaking##1
2. Food:mango == Hobby:card-games##1
3. Hobby:drawing is on the right of Hobby:filmmaking##1
4. Food:pepper is on the left of Hobby:card-games##1
5. Food:raspberry is on the left of Hobby:filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Hobby   | gardening  | filmmaking     | drawing   | card-games |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
Game: chess, mah-jongg, bridge, poker
1. Hobby:woodworking == Game:mah-jongg##1
2. Hobby:camping is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:cooking is on the right of Hobby:woodworking##1
4. Hobby:woodworking is on the right of Game:bridge##1
5. Game:mah-jongg is on the left of Game:chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Game   | bridge    | mah-jongg      | chess | poker |

